name: Horologium
description:
Horologium is an interactive clock for those who don't mind about numbers. There are 6 styles, 3 in of them in color and 3 in monochrome. Tap/Click to change the style and hit 'S' or 's' to save your preferred setting so next time when you open it , it is loaded with  your preferred setting. Settings are stored in browsers cache.
